title: Jabari Smith Jr. and RJ Barrett Put in Extra Work | Upside High
description:
J. Kyle Mann and Jonathan Tjarks are back to discuss the young and exciting players of the NBA, beginning with the pedigree and story of Jabari Smith Jr. (01:42). They then take it to New York and RJ Barrett to assess where they see him in his development and where he is headed (21:28).
Hosts: J. Kyle Mann and Jonathan Tjarks
Producer: Steve Ahlman
